channel.description: Posts in the discussion thread "National Shark Week" - its that time of year again, where we say, "Hi! ... Please don't eat me!" to our nautical fish-buddies

item.title: National Shark Week
item.content:encoded: As many of you know, it is national shark week. In that spirit, I direct you to the ninja-shark in Naruto Episode #189. Rock on my scaley friends!
